(window.webpackJsonp=window.webpackJsonp||[]).push([[62],{285:function(e){e.exports={data:{post:{title:"Can't hold on much longer",content:'<p>This stinks.</p>\n<p>I am used to rejection, but this is getting absurd.</p>\n<p><a href="/assets/static/src/media/images/blog/storyofmylife.gif"><img class="g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill=\'none\' viewBox=\'0 0 1280 323\' xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' xmlns:xlink=\'http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id=\'__svg-blur-0\'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in=\'SourceGraphic\' stdDeviation=\'40\'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x=\'0\' y=\'0\' filter=\'url(%23__svg-blur-0)\' width=\'1280\' height=\'323\' xlink:href=\'data:image/gif%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAQCAIAAAAphe5%2bAAAACXBIWXMAAAPoAAAD6AG1e1JrAAADQklEQVRIx9VWWW7bQAz1/Y/R/DVA20P4qy2SJrYsW7tk7Ztra9dYUt9wHCcNGhRoEyAmBgKHIofLI0eaDeM4TNNINP0TwfD4SvTS%2beI5DANjTGj2fS/4WXU4eCupKEuIoihSFEXXdcMwFEXVNA28Y9ue5%2bFVHMcRUZIkWZaBCcMwiZOmaaaHEvwPIb40TV3XtW3bsqw0zYQ7CC3LrqoK4cJX4Aee61ZlGUdxWZSzuigCTWua9lAcdE3fKIrjOFtnixzAZGmKcBF6QoSIgyAAs9vt8jzPiJD59BqEHPb7fUyENMDDBa9RkqCObdsiQyQQxREKWhQFYkBWM2Fc1zXigYHQm94rDUTnpgV/SqDt2L6si6op6xaddYb1WYX%2bKH8LOvf9Xz3OxJvdobaDXHXipeYfSurp6TLohABQYccBaxQMn2%2b%2b7RjHCdueJHh2PeNPugLAQKclpZ7xBabpuAJjQ932DZZQHei0ntHihmJBgQnbnvOnA3vWkho9Gc4XvoRr2g5PEBhPCNwr3o%2bNq22Tpe4DCtNLZTO827iSHugQar5ix1i36%2b1S9SUjBH8jO3j1VbIdQm9jRTjhTnEBpuVlC9WH%2bb3qSUawtqKNHa2MEDqyEao2V1ad5EbeQhlO4R0nw9fGitdmCBc4H4xsRhBqTmJ6maT5lp/dqV6cF9RgT1poXzbwvVC9e4XnYLjpikIUEcN%2bZQRwjHAXmicbASL4LjnQlykm0%2bXZImccUlSdgPRcpKOAdBipqelGpyVa%2b7QduD50SO/c/TzKkc/u4ywMv8/DqYU4vtQJR67LzcDwLUkg66m9wDBCmXA/tRD3Sg6EvsCXgpie%2bXuLO%2bARAdRyyTHKN3aMSn%2bTbFQUpRXDDQlHwE0UQh/gYtl%2bbvsZqg6hxhUCk0MXQB/9A9zWZgS55sQcUh3mKWzRLTjzlYeYrlheZlFvlLmoWlFmTGHbienpwWC2Opqkhoapo0FsaHseUDAPW26IaW65BB9/8aqvm/71ECAI8n2FhvbjnyjVQvNROdGUF3CNigSSXTm/1dE2S83L9iU%2bauyFX6t3%2bh3AFLJhqvuhP17KF%2bzZDIyTLMtfPn%2b6uvrw8fp6Pp97rne8BBB%2bAYAEomDlBtxJAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC\' /%3e%3c/svg%3e" width="1280" alt="One of many." data-srcset="/assets/static/storyofmylife.82a2fbd.415b8e4.gif 480w, /assets/static/storyofmylife.cbab2cf.415b8e4.gif 1024w" data-sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" data-src="/assets/static/storyofmylife.cbab2cf.415b8e4.gif"><noscript><img class="g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded" src="/assets/static/storyofmylife.cbab2cf.415b8e4.gif" width="1280" alt="One of many."></noscript></a>\n<em>One of many.</em></p>\n<p>Over and over again I get turned down for roles with a generic mail merge response. The most annoying thing is how positive I feel all the interviews go. I get along well with the people plus I am familiar with every scenario and software environment that is brought up. I’d like to think I could learn something from each and every interview, but even with a time machine I have no idea how I could go back and change things to improve my chances. I almost wish I was crashing and burning so I could clearly see how I would improve things for next time.</p>\n<p>Am I doing something wrong? Ugh, probably not. There is a whole boatload of people after work in this city, only the most arrogant would assume they are automatically the best person for a job.</p>\n<p>Right now my savings are melting away as I pay for rent and living out of the savings. I get up every morning and get on my good old Chuwi to investigate any new job listings that have popped up. I craft a nice cover letter for whatever listings I think I have a 1% chance of getting, hit submit and wait. I also try to follow up, but not being annoying is key when seeking employment.</p>\n<p>I also have a little bit of a cough. Not too bad, but enough to be a pain. It doesn’t help that my rented place can get a bit damp, requiring the windows to be open during the day to help dry it out. If I can hold out to summer I’m sure this place will be great, though.</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4fo__Sh0nIg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">I know I can’t hold on much longer</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4fo__Sh0nIg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">…but I will never let go</a></p>\n<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4fo__Sh0nIg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">I know that it’s a one way track</a> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4fo__Sh0nIg" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">…tell me now how long this’ll last</a></p>\n<p>Wasn’t 1999 such a simpler time? I would start playing Sonic Adventure, but I’m sure I’d be disappointed that it doesn’t live up to how I remember it. At least I have this beautiful framed piece of art on my wall to keep my spirits up.</p>\n<p><a href="/assets/static/src/media/images/blog/IMG_20170919_130623.jpg"><img class="g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill=\'none\' viewBox=\'0 0 1920 1440\' xmlns=\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\' xmlns:xlink=\'http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id=\'__svg-blur-24\'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in=\'SourceGraphic\' stdDeviation=\'40\'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x=\'0\' y=\'0\' filter=\'url(%23__svg-blur-24)\' width=\'1920\' height=\'1440\' xlink:href=\'data:image/jpeg%3bbase64%%2bapQ7Twfes1MfWwEcWoXBW2e4qNlU9sVnVn4tbowLnS7wMAMkSo35FEr4p6XIG8yyu0IGeYkP4aq3%2bMyLu4teSrR0ljHNBTIKWv1H0SRlQxXSOxACm3YE5%2bAxq30vV7HV7%2bazgaRZ4omlZSrAgKM85HB5H9aQeHlEPvL7nxcIOaz/wAQbxLOa0UpGzMrEFzwORWgK3mQK57kVmPia9uurWnqIw5WLA4zgEnP4qdBuOAs0Z6WjSguuIRL0LrKNnabVwcfarKIdqg6vQt0TrIHJ9JJj%2b2rMYphEHYnnjWdDhsrGyuLJN0UqBNxYlQ%2bfnnHvihepNHXTijRyRPJKA7ImDgZOSCOAPYd%2badbGW4k0qI315aIVVGSJEKyAg5%2bo/3iimXSNYUesd45ZAWVkC7E7Zz8nA79s1rDlCx3GFVJzxG6CcSm7/aiHpej2MKB7q5BWQD05XcG3Hn24P04p56DsmtbzVZkVtkllM7vIuHL5A55J7Y71R39o8F36KFmuoIRvhkSE7oyOdvH3xmnjpXT7m20LVrm6AXNkQEA/hyR3P1NJyWL9jf7%2bwlZSBqjr7%2boNAn7RPtWe9WRibX50dQ%2byNNoxkjitMijItI/tVFrGlWtyXeW3jaRhgtjBI%2b9ZGNZUxqbBEBxUmsQG86d1C2iAaWWB0Vc4ySKhjfipC%2baoXRuJ8yl0rRbC1skjvUgkm2gOGw547DgV2dB0HzN8ejwMxXaSIQBjvjmrkFR2ArhcU5sxb0Jyjp8EwDyhEu23s4Il/76AUDercPbywvKqwyDa6ouMj%2bdW8jg5qvuyMGgZ3byZ6ABF%2beIRoFHYUoeJV1caV0nd3tk6JNGExuTcDlgMf57063WCayLxG12W/0FtObYwlu4kVxwcB84%2be1DjXc5jc//2Q==\' /%3e%3c/svg%3e" width="1920" alt="All Mighty Hedgehog." data-srcset="/assets/static/IMG_20170919_130623.82a2fbd.711ba1f.jpg 480w, /assets/static/IMG_20170919_130623.cbab2cf.711ba1f.jpg 1024w, /assets/static/IMG_20170919_130623.2665e34.711ba1f.jpg 1920w" data-sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" data-src="/assets/static/IMG_20170919_130623.2665e34.711ba1f.jpg"><noscript><img class="g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded" src="/assets/static/IMG_20170919_130623.2665e34.711ba1f.jpg" width="1920" alt="All Mighty Hedgehog."></noscript></a>\n<em>All Mighty Hedgehog.</em></p>\n<p><a href="mailto:aaronights@gmail.com" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Email me with offers and advice: aaronights@gmail.com.</a></p>\n',date:"2017-09-18T00:00:00.000Z",timeToRead:2}}}}}]);